               <msContents>
                  <summary>Mǝ‘raf, chants, ምዕራፍ፡</summary>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1v" to="2r" facs="002">Fols 1v–2r</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1544Gebrah">Gǝbra Ḥǝmāmāt</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ለከ፡ ኃይል፡ ክብር፡ ወሰጊድ፡ እስከ፡ ለዓለም፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="2r" to="2v" facs="002">Fols 2r–2v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat Prayer against Snake, ጸሎተ፡ ዓርዌ፡ ምድር፡</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ጸሎተ፡ አርዌ፡ ምድር፡ ሐሰውኩ፡ በል፡ ፫ ጊዜ፡ ወለእመኒ፡ ዘነሰኮ፡ ከይሲ፡ አስትዮ፡ ለላእኩ በኃይሉ፡ ወበስመ እግዚአብሔር፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="3r" to="72v" facs="003">Fols 3r–72v, </locus><locus from="73v" to="74v" facs="074">73v–74v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3186Meeraf">Mǝʿrāf</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ምዕራፍ፡ ዘዮሐንስ፡ እስከ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ግዕዝ፡ ዋዜማ፡ ቅዱስ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ቅዱስ፡ ኃያል፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4"><locus from="73r" facs="073">Fols 73r and following</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat Prayer against Evil Eye, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ዓይን:</foreign></title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ:<gap reason="omitted"/> እንተ፡ ዓይን፡ ፃእ፡ በቀይሕ፡</incipit></msItem>
